Project rules:
- [Rust conventions] Prefer map_err over match for error transformation. Use ? for propagation.
- [API design] All handlers must return Result<Json<T>, RouteError>. Include StatusCode only for non-200 responses.
- [Testing] Use static fixtures parsed from JSON, not dynamically generated data. Group tests by function under test.
